    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/03d3bcec7396f117aef871dde3d062cf.avif?t=1754030663\" width=914 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/263ca5c9f15201bb3073eaa9151c6861.avif?t=1754030663\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/8a5982b5d09be406276b56f7d4106943.avif?t=1754030663\" width=311 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>愚者之梦：零时将至</strong>》是一款由零点世界（Zero world）工作室制作并发行的视觉小说游戏。游戏通过点击鼠标来进行故事推动，以便更加沉浸的体验故事。游戏文本量为12万字左右，单线单结局。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/e3f5ac8018b4a1aadf93e53d9b0cec4c.avif?t=1754030663\" width=311 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/b0d538dabbf3cd3ed8d0f56460ab6de8.avif?t=1754030663\" width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/719bc5d5c369fe4c2ba6269a182d2ffd.avif?t=1754030663\" width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/23663cea2d627ac774a9e3618417814e.avif?t=1754030663\" width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/2e6885c0a9f762c946440db068800dc4.avif?t=1754030663\" width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/c455c1ee74b6aecc01af20551d97d68e.avif?t=1754030663\" width=311 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >菲尔在多年前被旅行的魔女从战乱的城市带至遥远乡村，作为村子里的问题儿童，只有一位青梅竹马愿意与之相伴。直到某一天，菲尔在遇见了一位失去一切记忆来到村子的陌生少女后，倒悬在过去的命运开始运转，为了弄清楚零点城的真相，三人决定前往魔法大学，而少年成为旅者的故事才刚刚开始……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/6cd777f694ae47b2e7431ea73d519d24.avif?t=1754030663\" width=311 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏制作人：孤独爱上了夜晚</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧本原案：黑佐年</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立绘美术：小可乐，AuraMage</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG美术：超新星南瓜人，AuraMage</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q版美术：MTA-TA</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景美术：creator，三思等于34</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI美术：Resher鸢栀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音频后期：w小璃</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/2f0d959fe7af6b4a33e0e0b25bc8caa9.avif?t=1754030663\" width=311 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏制作人：孤独爱上了夜晚</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧本原案：黑佐年</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立绘美术：小可乐，AuraMage</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CG美术：超新星南瓜人，AuraMage</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景美术：creator，三思等于34</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配音副导演：w小璃</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV：薇薇安-阿贝花，莉安娜-冬绫，简妮斯-邢吱，浅兰-w小璃</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音频后期：w小璃</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI美术：予薇Werin</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特别感谢：秋璃，羽尘，北风陆南风伍，依目青图</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220070/extras/3da1b559ef0ad7a16926198259cfa5c1.avif?t=1754030663\" width=311 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UI：BOOTH空想曲线</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐：<strong>DOVA-SYNDROME</strong></p>",
